@host = http://localhost:5000

### What was declined and why (per project)
GET {{host}}/projects/Payments/declined

### What are the technical limitations (per project)
GET {{host}}/projects/Payments/limitations

### Manual sync: ingest in-repo knowledge artifacts from a local clone
POST {{host}}/ingest/repo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "Payments",
  "repoPath": "/path/to/local/clone",
  "source": "GitHub"
}
